Blueprint#NVIDIA NeMo Microservices Used":[41,49],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#NVIDIA NeMo Microservices Used#{1}":[43,43],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#NVIDIA NeMo Microservices Used#{2}":[44,44],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#NVIDIA NeMo Microservices Used#{3}":[45,45],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#NVIDIA NeMo Microservices Used#{4}":[46,46],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#NVIDIA NeMo Microservices Used#{5}":[47,47],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#NVIDIA NeMo Microservices Used#{6}":[48,49],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#NIM Models":[50,57],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#NIM Models#{1}":[52,52],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#NIM Models#{2}":[53,53],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#NIM Models#{3}":[54,54],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#NIM Models#{4}":[55,55],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#NIM Models#{5}":[56,57],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#System Requirements":[58,67],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#System Requirements#{1}":[60,67],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#Software Stack":[68,76],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#Software Stack#{1}":[70,70],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#Software Stack#{2}":[71,71],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#Software Stack#{3}":[72,72],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#Software Stack#{4}":[73,73],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#Software Stack#{5}":[74,74],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#Software Stack#{6}":[75,76],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#Related":[77,85],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#Related#{1}":[79,79],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#Related#{2}":[80,80],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#Related#{3}":[81,82],"#AI Orchestration for Data Flywheel Blueprint#Related#{4}":[83,85]},"outlinks":[{"title":"Iguazio MLRun's","target":"low-code orchestration engine with [NVIDIA NeMo microservices]( This enables a production-integrated data flywheel that fully automates end-to-end orchestration of continuous agent optimization.\n\n## MLRun: The Orchestrator\n\n[MLRun]( is an open-source AI orchestration framework built by Iguazio — acquired by QuantumBlack, AI by McKinsey. It acts as the orchestrator that:\n- Streamlines data collection\n- Partitions traffic for training and evaluation\n- Dispatches fine-tuning or evaluation jobs using NeMo microservices\n- Exposes intuitive APIs and minimizes boilerplate code\n\n## Key Features\n\n1. **Unified AIOps Orchestration**: MLRun automates data flows, logging, job scheduling, finetuning and evaluation - simplifying CI/CD integration.\n\n2. **Live, Low-Code Optimization**: Continuously adapts models to production data with minimal effort to reduce latency, TCO, and manual tuning — while cutting boilerplate code up to 90%.\n\n3. **Plug-and-Play Flexibility**: Modular APIs and low-code setup integrate easily across cloud, hybrid, or on-prem stacks.\n\n4. **Integrated Evaluation and Tuning**: NeMo microservices exposed as simple-to-use APIs, orchestrated by MLRun, handle SFT-LoRA tuning and automated evaluations.\n\n## NVIDIA NeMo Microservices Used\n\n- **NeMo Customizer**: Model finetuning\n- **NeMo Evaluator**: Model and workflow evaluation\n- **Datastore**: Stores datasets, evaluation results, fine-tuning artifacts\n- **Deployment Manager**: Deploys and experiments with candidate models\n- **Entity Store**: Unified data model and registry\n- **NIM Proxy**: Routes inference across multiple models\n\n## NIM Models\n\n- llama-3.3-70b-instruct\n- llama-3.2-1b-instruct\n- llama-3.2-3b-instruct\n- llama-3.1-70b-instruct\n- llama-3.1-8b-instruct\n\n## System Requirements\n\n| Component | Requirement |\n|-----------|-------------|\n| Hardware (Self-hosted LLM Judge","line":21},{"title":"ai-observability-for-data-flywheel-by-weights-biases","target":"ai-observability-for-data-flywheel-by-weights-biases","line":79},{"title":"rag-concept","target":"rag-concept","line":80},{"title":"cyborg-enterprise-rag-blueprint","target":"cyborg-enterprise-rag-blueprint","line":81}],"metadata":{"created":"2026-04-05","tags":["#rag","#ai-orchestration","#data-flywheel","#mlrun","#nvidia-blueprint"]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},"smart_blocks:WIKI/raw/ai-orchestration-for-data-flywheel-by-iguazio.md#---frontmatter---": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":null},"embeddings":{},"text":null,"length":0,"last_read":{"hash":"11ntrab","at":1776764153485},"key":"WIKI/raw/ai-orchestration-for-data-flywheel-by-iguazio.md#---frontmatter---","lines":[1,9],"size":121,"outlinks":[],"class_name":"SmartBlock"},
